The body of late Rev. Fr. Cosmas Ahamefula Ekwuribe was on Thursday laid to rest in Aba, Abia State. It was indeed a sad moment for members of the Catholic community and his immediate family members in the state as they were seen weeping and wailing over the death of their loved Reverend Father. According to ABN TV, the man of God passed on at the age of 39 in his sleep. His burial followed a requem mass celebrated at the Christ the King Cathedral, Aba by His Lordship, Most Rev. Prof. Augustine Ndubueze Echema, Catholic Bishop of Aba. See more photos: Source